line_1: His stomach baulk'd, now hunger gnaws;
line_2: Howling, he grinds his empty jaws;

line_1: On the firm Plate the fond Sea-Lamprey gnaws:
line_2: Madded with Pain, and crush'd by meeting Claws,

line_1: While its fierce teeth his tender body gnaws.
line_2: He grasps the dragon by th' invenom'd jaws,
